          <mainBody>
            <p eId="annex_1_p_8"><b>Annex A – Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>49 </num>
              <p>The Act extends to England, Wales and Northern Ireland, and applies in relation to England and Northern Ireland.</p>
            </blockContainer>
            <table uk:widths="1.18in 1.18in 1.18in 1.18in 1.18in">
              <tr>
                <td rowspan="2">
                  <p><b>Provision</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>England</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Wales</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Scotland</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Northern Ireland</b></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Extends to E &amp; W and applies to England?</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Extends to E &amp; W and applies to Wales?</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Extends and applies to Scotland?</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Extends and applies to Northern Ireland?</b></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Section 1 Dog abduction</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>No</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>No</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
